2
00:05:21.666 --> 00:05:22.625
Don't!

3
00:05:22.707 --> 00:05:23.791
Don't!

4
00:06:47.916 --> 00:06:51.666
Doctor. please my son has been shot.

5
00:06:51.750 --> 00:06:54.875
Look around you. Madame.
Everyone in Paris has been shot.

6
00:06:55.500 --> 00:06:57.875
I'm begging you.

7
00:07:00.750 --> 00:07:03.458
He'll die if you don't see him.

8
00:07:05.458 --> 00:07:08.208
Yes. Gold. Gold.

9
00:07:08.750 --> 00:07:11.500
Take it. For the revolution.

10
00:07:12.041 --> 00:07:14.875
But you must see my son straight away.

11
00:07:15.333 --> 00:07:16.250
Immediately!

12
00:07:20.750 --> 00:07:22.166
Let me see it.

13
00:07:23.291 --> 00:07:24.666
Nurse.

14
00:07:25.416 --> 00:07:27.791
Prepare this patient for surgery.

15
00:07:28.207 --> 00:07:29.957
You can't be in here now.

16
00:07:30.041 --> 00:07:31.291
You'll have to leave.

17
00:08:28.916 --> 00:08:30.332
How is he?

18
00:08:30.916 --> 00:08:33.707
I've done my best.

19
00:08:34.375 --> 00:08:36.540
It's up to him now.

20
00:14:22.208 --> 00:14:23.166
Hello.

21
00:14:23.458 --> 00:14:25.166
I could make you filthy rich.

22
00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:31.208
Would you mind?

23
00:14:43.250 --> 00:14:44.415
Excuse me.

24
00:14:45.415 --> 00:14:47.165
Do you know where this place is?

25
00:14:49.083 --> 00:14:50.040
No. Sorry. my love.

26
00:15:43.290 --> 00:15:44.915
You are a genius.

27
00:19:35.125 --> 00:19:36.583
The Duke D'Ormond.

28
00:21:07.166 --> 00:21:08.666
The Duke D'Ormond.

29
00:22:19.458 --> 00:22:20.291
Careful!

30
00:22:22.916 --> 00:22:23.750
I'm so sorry!

31
00:22:27.208 --> 00:22:30.250
Go and get your manager!

32
00:22:32.708 --> 00:22:33.666
I believe this is yours.

33
00:22:36.500 --> 00:22:37.708
I said I was sorry.

34
00:27:01.250 --> 00:27:03.416
-Good day. sir.
-How may I assist?

35
00:27:03.500 --> 00:27:05.875
That man who was just here.

36
00:27:08.000 --> 00:27:10.666
I want to see what he sent.

37
00:27:11.875 --> 00:27:12.708
Sir?

38
00:27:17.958 --> 00:27:19.166
For your trouble.

39
00:27:22.166 --> 00:27:24.541
Unless you'd like
to handle this another way?

40
00:27:26.375 --> 00:27:28.041
Sir? No?

41
00:27:33.958 --> 00:27:34.875
Good lad.

42
00:27:39.708 --> 00:27:40.583
What is this?

43
00:33:26.416 --> 00:33:28.708
Well done. Thank you. Burak.

